  "author": "XO_OX Designs",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Every drum uses a mismatched body model — djembe in a box, tabla in a cylinder, cajon open. The wrong bodies reveal hidden timbres. FIRE pushes further into wrongness.",
