  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OSTINATO — Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": [
      "Psalm 2: The Formant Whisper — body models create formant-like resonances at wrong frequencies"
    ],
    "revelation": "The Finger discovered that bodyModel override is the most underexplored parameter in OSTINATO. Djembe through a Box body (cajon resonance) creates a formant-vowel quality. Tabla through Cylindrical creates a sitar-like resonance. Every wrong body is a new instrument.",
    "god": "Resonara",
    "flock_note": "The Eye confirmed: frequency spectrum completely transforms with body swap. A djembe in an Open body becomes a frame drum hybrid. This is OSTINATO's secret synthesis mode — body model as instrument design parameter.",
    "diagnosis": "Body Swap was drums with wrong resonances. It is now a cabinet of instruments that do not exist — the djembe-cajon, the tabla-surdo, the bongo-frame. Wrong bodies as deliberate design."
  },
